Caretaker Chairman of Kaura Local Government Area, Dr. Bege Katuka, has been reportedly kidnapped. The Nation gathered the Local Government Council boss was seized by gunmen suspected to be kidnappers at his farm in Juji Village, Chikun LGA on Sunday. It was also gathered the gunmen killed the man who rode the chairman to the farm. The Nation gathered Katuka was on a commercial motorcycle when the kidnapper opened fire on the rider, killing him instantly before they whisked away their victim. It was learnt the abductors had not called for ransom as at the time of filing this report. Kaduna State Police Commandâ€™s Public Relation Officer, ASP Muhammad Jalige did not pick several calls to confirm the incident.